wiki.text:
'Ala' may refer to:
* Ala (demon), a female demon in Serbian and Bulgarian mythology
* Ala (Odinani), an Alusi in Odinani
* Ala (Roman allied military unit), a Republican-period, largely infantry,
  formation of 5,400 men
* Ala (Roman cavalry unit), an Imperial-period, purely cavalry, formation
  of 500 men

In 'language': *à la, French for 'in the style/manner of' commonly used in
English *Wing, Ala in Latin

* Ala, Trentino, a town in Trentino, Italy
* Ala dağları, a mountain range in the Taurus chain, Turkey
